high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the white table.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you above the orange cup.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Take a couple steps to your left to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Go left and cross the room and turn to the right and face the white table.
Pick the apple up from the table.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the apple up and shut the door again.
Go  left and turn to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go forward. Then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Turn around completely and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside. Chill the apple then take it out.
Step to the left then turn right to face the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.
